rescue your friend, was it?

01:46:38.480 --> 01:46:40.311
(CHOKING)

01:46:43.480 --> 01:46:44.959
(GROANING)

01:46:50.040 --> 01:46:51.632
(WHISTLES)

01:46:54.480 --> 01:46:56.675
(SCOFFS) Jake.

01:46:56.840 --> 01:46:58.176
