as long as I can.

01:46:58.200 --> 01:46:59.633
When are you
going to realize

01:46:59.720 --> 01:47:01.438
you are a terrible shot
with that thing.

01:47:01.560 --> 01:47:03.152
(BLOWS)
(SCREAMS)

01:47:03.280 --> 01:47:05.280
