them back to the Ghost Train.

01:51:18.880 --> 01:51:20.757
Jake needs us.
Barron's too strong.

01:51:22.880 --> 01:51:24.711
(SCREECHES)
(GROANS)

01:51:28.440 --> 01:51:29.919
