01:57:54.480 --> 01:57:56.038
Go to her, Jake.

01:57:57.640 --> 01:57:59.312
You have the map.

01:57:59.480 --> 01:58:02.472
You can get back to 1943.

01:58:05.000 --> 01:58:07.639
